text: Florentin Durand (born 9 November 1982) is a French ski jumper. He competed in the large hill event at the 2002 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:French male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of France Category:Ski jumpers at the 2002 Winter Olympics Category:People from Saint-Martin-d'Hères
